---
title: Roasted Cauliflower and Squash Tacos with Crunchy Jicama Slaw and Yogurt Crema
description: We're in love with this vegetarian taco. The sweet roasted veggies pair extraordinarily well with the zesty jicama slaw and citrusy yogurt! If you've never tried jicama, you're in for a treat. This root vegetable has a mild, refreshing flavour and fun, crunchy texture!
